					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p97879">Re: MMC3 (or similar) reproduction circuit boards anyone?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=97879#p97879"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Aug 09, 2012 10:33 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
